data.subject: The Lord`s Prayer (Remastered)
data.lyric:
Our Father
 Who art in heaven
 Hallowed be Thy name
 Thy kingdom come
 Thy will be done
 On earth as

data.subject: Silent Night (Remastered)
data.lyric:
Silent night, holy night
 All is calm, all is bright
 Round yon Virgin Mother and Child
 Holy Infant
